sequenceDiagram
    actor Initiator
    actor UBOs
    participant EUDIWallet_Initiator
    participant Company_Wallet
    participant TR
    participant Bank_System
    participant Bank_Wallet
    participant Bank_InternalSystem

    activate Initiator

    Note over Initiator,Bank_Wallet: Scenario 1

    Initiator->>+Bank_System: Select "open business account"
    critical LegalEntity Selection
    option Option1.Support_EUBW_Directory_List
        Bank_System->>+Bank_System : Provide the list of available legal entities
        Initiator->>+Bank_System: select the legal entity from the list & the respective wallet address
        Bank_System->>+Bank_System: resolve the endpoint of selected legal entity
    option Option2.Support_EndPoint (address or endpoint URI)
        Bank_System->>+Bank_System : Provide an input field
        Initiator->>+Bank_System: fill the address or end-point of the business wallet
        Bank_System->>+Bank_System: resolve the endpoint of the address
    option Option3.Support directly into EUBW
        Note over Company_Wallet: the company wallet already integrate the business process of specific banks
        Initiator->>+Company_Wallet: Select bank in the EUBW (configured in wallet)
    option Option4. Other: manual process (EUBW or EUDI Wallet)
        Note over Company_Wallet: manuall proces by the initiator
    end
    Initiator->>+Bank_System: trigger process

    Note over Initiator,Bank_Wallet: Initiator Identification
    Bank_System<<->>Bank_Wallet: generate request to identity initiator (PID)
    Bank_System->>+Bank_Wallet: embed request into QRCode
    Initiator->>+EUDIWallet_Initiator : Scan the code
    Initiator->>+EUDIWallet_Initiator : mutual auth ( over auth. certificate)
    EUDIWallet_Initiator->Bank_System : send the pid information
    Bank_System<<->>Bank_Wallet: verification of PID  (rulebook)

    Note over Initiator,Bank_Wallet: LegalEntity Identification
    Bank_System<<->>Bank_Wallet: generate request for EBWOID, EUCC,TAX, VAT, CompanyInfo, ContactPerson
    critical
    option Automatically (EUBW support end-points)
        Bank_System->>+Company_Wallet: request presentations
        Company_Wallet<<->>Company_Wallet: check the request authorization (automatically acceptance)
        Company_Wallet->>Bank_System: present the attestations
    option Manually ( EUBW or EUDI Wallet)
        Bank_System->>Bank_System: embed request into QRCode and provide a DeepLink for the request
        Initiator->>+Company_Wallet: copy/paste deep-link presentation into the company wallet or scan the QRCode
        Company_Wallet->>+Company_Wallet: check the request authorization (manual process)
        Company_Wallet->>Bank_System: present the attestations
    end
    Bank_System<<->>Bank_Wallet: verification of attestations rulebooks
    Bank_System<<->>Bank_System: Optional: check if the legal repr. is part of the EUCC

    Note over Initiator,Bank_Wallet: Addtionally KYC information
    Bank_System<<->>Bank_Wallet: generate request for OwnershipList, Controllist, UBOList, SignatoryRights

    critical
    option Automatically (EUBW support end-points)
        Bank_System->>+Company_Wallet: request presentations
        Company_Wallet<<->>Company_Wallet: check the request authorization (automatically acceptance)
        Company_Wallet->>Bank_System: present the attestations
    option Manually ( EUBW or EUDI Wallet)
        Bank_System->>Bank_System: embed request into QRCode and provide a DeepLink for the request
        Initiator->>+Company_Wallet: copy/paste deep-link presentation into the company wallet or scan the QRCode
        Company_Wallet->>+Company_Wallet: check the request authorization (manual process)
        Company_Wallet->>Bank_System: present the attestations
    end
    Bank_System<<->>Bank_Wallet: verification of attestations (rulebook)

    Note right of Bank_System: Perform UBO Calculation based on the OwnerShip/ControlList
    Bank_System->>Bank_System: additionally check UBO List(calculated) vs UBO List (Company) and in case of discrepancies inform the company

    Note over Initiator,Bank_Wallet: Additionally KYC information from Transparency Register
    Bank_System<<->>Bank_Wallet: generate request for UBOList (TR)
    critical
    option Option1. From Company Wallet
        Bank_System->>+Company_Wallet: request presentations
        Company_Wallet<<->>Company_Wallet: check the request authorization (automatically acceptance)
        Company_Wallet->>Bank_System: present the attestations
    option Option2. From Transaprency Register
        Bank_System->>+TR: request presentations
        TR<<->>TR: check the request authorization (automatically acceptance)
        TR->>Bank_System: present the attestations
    end
    Bank_System<<->>Bank_Wallet: verification of attestations (rulebook)
    Bank_System->>Bank_System: additionally check UBO List(calculated) vs UBO List (TR) and in case of discrepancies inform the TR

    Note over Initiator,Bank_Wallet: UBO Verification
    Bank_System<<->>Bank_System: Start UBO Identity Verification for each UBO in the list
    Bank_System->>Initiator: generate link and send it
    critical
    option for each ubo person in the list
        UBOs->>Bank_System: open the link
        Bank_System<<->>Bank_Wallet: generate request for PID and embed into QRCode
        UBOs->>UBOs: scan the code using the own wallet and present the PID
        Bank_System<<->>Bank_Wallet: verification of PID (rulebook verication)
        Bank_System<<->>Bank_System: additionally verification PID data against UBO data
    end

    Bank_System<<->>Bank_System: cross check over all attestations
    Bank_System->>+Bank_InternalSystem: transfer data to internal system

    Note over Initiator,Bank_Wallet: Scenario2 (contract signing)


    Note over Initiator,Bank_Wallet: Scenario3 (IBAN Issuing)